name: VE-7000 Complete System
description:
The VE-7000 is Vadaenergy's 
latest creation in hho technology.
It is 40% more efficient over the
Max series generators.

Our new construction improves
on all levels.

High hho output, low current draw,
much cooler long term operation. 
Long life expectancy and low
maintenance.

We are confident that our VE series 
generators are of the best
for quality vs price.  

Made with high grade,
deep draw stainless steel plates.
EPDM long life gasket separators.
High density end plats.  
All stainless steel hardware. 
High current Bolt power Studs.
3/8 barb fittings. 

Generator dimensions: 
9"W 9"H 2"D (including hardware)

This kit contains the VE-7000
generator plus:

1.5 qt reservoir bottle with cap
12 feet of clear high quality hose
Cooper cooler 
Wiring harness
Baggie of KOH *Use extra care when
 handling corrosive substances
10 14" zip ties
Installation manual 
 

This is ready to install, includes 
everything you see on the pictures

Fully assembled with an 
instruction manual

Some knowledge about the auto 
electrical system is required for installation
